  "title": "Crisp Korean Tempeh Skillet",
  "description": "A one-pot Korean dish featuring tempeh, lacquer-glaze, and roasted vegetables, served on a talavera plate. This vegetarian-friendly dish is perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
