  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the tempeh and cook until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the soy sauce, gochujang, and brown sugar, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the bell peppers and onions, and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the green onions and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Serve the skillet hot, garnished with additional green onions if desired.",
    "Place the skillet on a talavera plate and serve immediately."
